  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We did it for the `showMore.templates` as well. And here we even had several templates (`active` / `inactive`).\n\nI remember discussing it with @vvo at some point, and we more or less agreed that using a subobject was better, but we never wrote any standard for that. I'm open for discussing it\n",
